<title>USA: Synopsys promotes Chan within sr mgmnt.</title>
<headline>Synopsys promotes Chan within sr mgmnt.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Synopsys Inc said Chi-Foon Chan was named to the newly formed position of chief operating officer, office of the President.</p>
<p>As part of the Office of the President, Chan continues to share responsibility for running the company with Synopsys Chief Executive Aart de Geus.</p>
<p>Chan was formerly executive vice president, office of the president.</p>
<p>Chan's appointment was part of several executive appointments and promotions in senior management, sales, marketing and engineering.</p>
